            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "The triggering of `CursorHold` depends on the `updatetime` setting, which defaults to 4000. If user does not set a lower value, this means they must keep the cursor stationary for a considerable amount of time before the diagnostic virtual line becomes visible. Merging this change as-is could potentially confuse some users.it would be best to update the doc accordingly.",
